supplementary-material.p: T cell responses directed against YFV or JEV antigens in ELISpot assay. Representative wells of ELISpot assays showing TNF-α (A) and IFN-γ (B and C) production by splenocytes of AG129 mice (A and B) and C57BL/6 mice (C) at 18 and 4 weeks, respectively, after vaccination with 10 4 PFU JE-CVax, following 16 h of ex vivo restimulation with an MHC class I-restricted peptide derived from YFV NS3 32 or the lysate of YFV-17D- or JEV SA14-14-2-infected Vero E6 cells. Stimulation using lysate of noninfected Vero E6 cells served as a negative control. Download FIG S4, JPG file, 0.3 MB.
